If Only It Were True (original title: Si seulement c'Ã©tait vrai...) is French author Marc Levy's first novel, released in 1999. It was translated into English in 2000 and was adapted into the American film Just Like Heaven in 2005. A 2006 Bollywood movie named I See You is also an adaptation of this book. A Malayalam film Vismayathumbathu with a similar theme was released in 2004. The inspiration of which may be this novel.